# Entity Pattern

- Immutable тАФ all fields `final`, prefer `const` constructor
- Include `fromJson`, `toJson`, `copyWith`
- Use Equatable for value comparison
- Use nullable types for optional fields
- Handle type casting explicitly in `fromJson`

## Response Wrapper

Use `ApiResponse<T>` in `domain/entities/common/` for API wrappers.

## Navigation Args

Pass screen arguments via constructor, not `ModalRoute.settings.arguments`.
